Our Brand Is Crisis;;75;;93;;NC;;Bolivia is on the brink of a violent coup d'etat, but that can't stop the political strategy team of GCS -- Greenberg Carville Shrum -- from putting together a slick American style re-election campaign for unpopular presidential candidate Gonzalo "Goni" Sanchez de Lozada. Featuring unprecedented access, this documentary follows Clinton administration political strategist James Carville as he leads a media assault team from the back rooms of Washington, D.C., to La Paz, the capital of Bolivia.;;Documentary;;Rachel Boynton;;2005;;NC;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/our_brand_is_crisis